msgid "# Test-HgsServer"
msgstr "# 测试 HGS 服务器"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid ""
"Tests if the local computer can function as a Host Guardian Service server "
"node."
msgstr "测试本地计算机是否能够作为Host Guardian Service服务器节点运行。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "### PrimaryServer_HgsDomain (Default)"
msgstr "### PrimaryServer_HgsDomain（默认值）"

msgid "### AdditionalServer"
msgstr "### AdditionalServer"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 描述"

msgid ""
"The **Test-HgsServer** cmdlet obtains information about the features, "
"configuration, and state of the local computer, and compares it with the "
"recommended settings to determine whether it can function as a Host Guardian"
" Service (HGS) server node."
msgstr ""
"`Test-HgsServer` cmdlet 可以获取有关本地计算机的功能、配置和状态的信息，并将其与推荐设置进行比较，以确定该计算机是否可以作为 "
"Host Guardian Service (HGS) 服务器节点正常运行。"

msgid "The following checks are performed, when applicable:"
msgstr "在适用的情况下，会执行以下检查："

msgid ""
"For more information about the scenario terms, see [Security and "
"Assurance](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=699209)."
msgstr ""
"有关场景术语的更多信息，请参阅[安全与保障](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=699209)。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid "### Example 1: Test the first HGS node"
msgstr "### 示例 1：测试第一个 HGS 节点"

msgid ""
"This command tests whether the local computer can be used as the first HGS "
"node."
msgstr "此命令用于测试本地计算机是否可以充当第一个HGS节点。"

msgid "### Example 2: Test an additional HGS node"
msgstr "### 示例 2：测试另一个 HGS 节点"

msgid ""
"This command tests whether the local computer can be used as an additional "
"HGS node."
msgstr "此命令用于测试本地计算机是否可以作为额外的 HGS 节点使用。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid "Specifies a database path."
msgstr "指定一个数据库路径。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the Active Directory domain administrator credentials for the "
"primary HGS server."
msgstr "指定用于主HGS服务器的Active Directory域管理员凭据。"

msgid "Specifies the name of the Active Directory domain for the HGS server."
msgstr "指定用于 HGS 服务器的 Active Directory 域的名称。"

msgid "Specifies the network IP address for the HGS server."
msgstr "指定 HGS 服务器的网络 IP 地址。"

msgid "Specifies the output log directory."
msgstr "指定输出日志文件的目录。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the password for the administrator account when the computer is "
"started in Safe Mode or a variant of Safe Mode, such as Directory Services "
"Restore Mode."
msgstr "当计算机在安全模式（或安全模式的变体，例如目录服务恢复模式）下启动时，该设置用于指定管理员账户的密码。"

msgid "### CommonParameters"
msgstr "### CommonParameters"

msgid ""
"This cmdlet supports the common parameters: -Debug, -ErrorAction, "
"-ErrorVariable, -InformationAction, -InformationVariable, -OutVariable, "
"-OutBuffer, -PipelineVariable, -Verbose, -WarningAction, and "
"-WarningVariable. For more information, see about_CommonParameters "
"(http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113216)."
msgstr ""
"此 cmdlet "
"支持以下常用参数：-Debug、-ErrorAction、-ErrorVariable、-InformationAction、-InformationVariable、-OutVariable、-OutBuffer、-PipelineVariable、-Verbose、-WarningAction"
" 和 "
"-WarningVariable。有关更多信息，请参阅关于COMMONParameters（http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113216）。"

